妹嘅人會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"早產可以早D出返黎見ONCE"},{"pid":"41cce97d5b495e9a4fa807fa84c015ad5ae50511","tid":1330064,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"呢個已經係導清喺mina出事之後嘅第10個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc595748be0957d0c36a19ab80fba9755bfbe8f5","tid":1330064,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41cce97d5b495e9a4fa807fa84c015ad5ae50511","tid":1330064,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"呢個已經係導清喺mina出事之後嘅第10個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"食屎狗黎 成日反我地twice"},{"pid":"40ed55f0cd6134d660f4c9f629011111f7624b14","tid":1330064,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"走咗個咪搵後備頂上囉，反正個樣一樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052439463300641c7d77dd40cea2e47bb340acfc","tid":1330064,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc595748be0957d0c36a19ab80fba9755bfbe8f5","tid":1330064,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41cce97d5b495e9a4fa807fa84c015ad5ae50511","tid":1330064,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"呢個已經係導清喺mina出事之後嘅第10個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-